  "abstract": "A long time champion of poor farmers in the semi-arid or dry tropics (SAT) of Asia and sub-Saharan\r\nAfrica (SSA), ICRISAT recognizes the need to include high value commodities and products in its\r\nresearch for development agenda. This is consistent with the CGIAR’s new research priority (3A) on\r\nreducing rural poverty through agriculture diversification and emerging opportunities for high value\r\ncommodities and products.\r\n",
